  m_text: You defeated the monster but you realized your submarine's robotic arm
    was too weak to lift its lifeless corpse. You quickly resurface, bringing nothing
    back, traumatized by the event and afraid that the thing might not truly be dead.
    You quit the job with no luck and your debt still remains unpaid.
